  "description": "Darker, more compressed EDM feel. The djembe delivers a subby kick replacement while beatbox locks in the grid. Doumbek fills in the offbeat subdivisions with rapid-fire precision. Low humanize keeps the machine feel but the CIRCLE amount creates a surging sympathetic pressure in the low frequencies — the feeling of standing next to a subwoofer stack.",
